HEADWORD: Abaculus
<hw>A*bac"u*lus</hw> <pr>(⟦adot⟧b*⟦acr⟧k"⟦usl⟧*l⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Abaculi</plw>
